  "link": "[P5520 [yLOI2019] 青原樱 - 洛谷](https://www.luogu.com.cn/problem/P5520)",
  "link_text": "[P5520 [yLOI2019] 青原樱 - 洛谷](https://www.luogu.com.cn/problem/P5520)",
